---
import ToolLayout from "../../layouts/ToolLayout.astro";

const title = 'YAML ? JSON Converter';
const description = 'Konversi YAML ke JSON dan JSON ke YAML online. Format data dengan cepat dan akurat.';
const keywords = 'yaml to json, json to yaml, yaml converter, yaml formatter';
const bodyHtml = `<header class="d-flex align-items-center gap-3 mb-4"><div class="tool-icon" style="background:#fefce8;color:#ca8a04;"><svg width="22" height="22" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M4 6h16M4 12h16M4 18h16"/></svg></div><div><h1 class="h3 mb-0">YAML ? JSON Converter</h1><p class="text-muted small mb-0">Konversi YAML ke JSON atau JSON ke YAML. Paste data, pilih arah, dan konversi.</p></div></header>
<div class="row g-4 mb-4">
<div class="col-lg-6"><label class="form-label fw-semibold">Input</label><textarea id="inputArea" class="form-control font-mono" rows="10" placeholder="Paste YAML atau JSON..."></textarea>
<div class="d-flex gap-2 mt-2"><button id="btnToJson" class="btn btn-primary">YAML ? JSON</button><button id="btnToYaml" class="btn btn-success">JSON ? YAML</button><button id="btnClear" class="btn btn-outline-danger">Clear</button></div></div>
<div class="col-lg-6"><div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-1"><label class="form-label fw-semibold mb-0">Output</label><button id="btnCopy" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-secondary">Copy</button></div>
<textarea id="outputArea" class="form-control font-mono" rows="10" readonly></textarea></div></div>
<div class="mt-4 p-3 rounded" style="background:var(--surface-soft);border:1px solid var(--border)"><h6 class="fw-bold">Tentang YAML ? JSON Converter</h6><p class="small mb-1" style="line-height:1.6">YAML to JSON dan JSON to YAML converter online untuk mengkonversi data antara dua format konfigurasi yang populer. YAML (YAML Ain't Markup Language) banyak digunakan untuk file konfigurasi karena lebih mudah dibaca manusia, sementara JSON lebih ringan dan banyak digunakan dalam API dan penyimpanan data. Alat ini mendukung konversi dua arah secara instan.</p><p class="small mb-0" style="line-height:1.6">Fitur konverter ini meliputi: konversi YAML ke JSON dengan indentasi yang rapi, konversi JSON ke YAML dengan format yang bersih, validasi syntax untuk kedua format, penanganan berbagai tipe data (string, number, boolean, null, array, object), dukungan untuk YAML multiline string, dan tombol copy untuk menyalin hasil. Preview hasil ditampilkan dalam editor yang nyaman dibaca.</p><p class="small mb-0 mt-2" style="line-height:1.6">YAML dan JSON converter sangat berguna dalam pengembangan perangkat lunak modern: mengkonversi file konfigurasi Docker Compose (YAML) ke format yang lebih mudah diproses, mengubah file konfigurasi aplikasi (YAML) untuk digunakan dengan API yang membutuhkan JSON, bekerja dengan Kubernetes manifest (YAML), CI/CD pipeline configuration (YAML), dan OpenAPI/Swagger specification yang sering menggunakan kedua format. Semua konversi dilakukan di browser.</p></div>`;
const extraHtml = `
<div class="mt-3 pt-2 d-flex gap-2 justify-content-center align-items-center">
<span class="small text-muted me-2">Bagikan:</span>
<a href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?url=" onclick="this.href+=encodeURIComponent(location.href)" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm rounded-pill" title="Twitter/X">&nearr;</a>
<a href="https://www.linkedin.com/sharing/share-offsite/?url=" onclick="this.href+=encodeURIComponent(location.href)" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm rounded-pill" title="LinkedIn">in</a>
<a href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=" onclick="this.href+=encodeURIComponent(location.href)" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm rounded-pill" title="Facebook">f</a>
<a href="https://api.whatsapp.com/send?text=" onclick="this.href+=encodeURIComponent(location.href)" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm rounded-pill" title="WhatsApp">wa</a>
</div>
<div class="mt-4 pt-2"><div class="small fw-semibold mb-2 text-muted">Alat Terkait</div><div class="d-flex gap-2 flex-wrap"><a href="json-formatter" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm rounded-pill">JSON Formatter</a><a href="json-csv" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm rounded-pill">JSON to CSV</a><a href="csv-viewer" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm rounded-pill">CSV Viewer</a><a href="html-preview" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm rounded-pill">HTML Preview</a></div>`;
---

<ToolLayout
  title={title}
  description={description}
  keywords={keywords}
>

<Fragment set:html={bodyHtml} />
<Fragment set:html={extraHtml} />

</ToolLayout>

<style is:inline>
.saweria-float { position: fixed; bottom: 24px; right: 24px; z-index: 9999; background: #ff6b6b; color: #fff; border-radius: 50px; padding: 10px 20px 10px 16px; text-decoration: none; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(255,107,107,0.4); transition: all 0.3s ease; font-family: "Inter",sans-serif; }
.saweria-float:hover { transform: translateY(-3px); box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(255,107,107,0.6); color: #fff; }
.saweria-float svg { animation: pulse 1.5s ease infinite; }
@keyframes pulse { 0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); } 50% { transform: scale(1.15); } }
@media (max-width: 576px) { .saweria-float { bottom: 16px; right: 16px; padding: 8px 14px 8px 10px; font-size: 12px; } }
</style>

<script is:inline>
document.getElementById('year').textContent=new Date().getFullYear();
</script>

<script is:inline>
var inp=document.getElementById('inputArea'),out=document.getElementById('outputArea');
function toJson(){try{var d=jsyaml.load(inp.value);out.value=JSON.stringify(d,null,2)}catch(e){out.value='Error: '+e.message}}
function toYaml(){try{var d=JSON.parse(inp.value);out.value=jsyaml.dump(d,{indent:2})}catch(e){out.value='Error: '+e.message}}
document.getElementById('btnToJson').addEventListener('click',toJson);
document.getElementById('btnToYaml').addEventListener('click',toYaml);
document.getElementById('btnClear').addEventListener('click',function(){inp.value='';out.value=''});
document.getElementById('btnCopy').addEventListener('click',function(){if(!out.value)return;var b=this;navigator.clipboard.writeText(out.value).then(function(){b.textContent='Copied!';setTimeout(function(){b.textContent='Copy'},1500)})});
</script>

<a href="https://saweria.co/naufalrakha" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="saweria-float" title="Donasi via Saweria">
